title: FC Kolos Bykovo
text: FC Kolos Bykovo () was a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> team from <a href="Bykovo%2C%20Volgograd%20Oblast">Bykovo, Volgograd Oblast</a>. It played professionally for one season in 1994 in the <a href="Russian%20Third%20League">Russian Third League</a>.
